## Testing Responsive Design

```ruby
test "shows mobile menu on small screens" do
  resize_window_to(375, 667)  # iPhone size
  visit root_url
  
  assert_selector "#mobile-menu-toggle"
  assert_no_selector "#desktop-menu"
  
  click_button "Menu"
  assert_selector "#mobile-menu.open"
end

test "shows desktop layout on large screens" do
  resize_window_to(1920, 1080)
  visit root_url
  
  assert_selector "#desktop-menu"
  assert_no_selector "#mobile-menu-toggle"
end

# Helper method in ApplicationSystemTestCase
def resize_window_to(width, height)
  page.driver.browser.manage.window.resize_to(width, height)
end
```

